thread.title: BRIEF-Lead Eastern Investment sees FY 2017 net profit down about 38.02 pct

author: Reuters Editorial
title: BRIEF-Lead Eastern Investment sees FY 2017 net profit down about 38.02 pct

organizations.name: reuters) - lead eastern investment co ltd

text:
Jan 31(Reuters) - Lead Eastern Investment Co Ltd :
* Sees FY 2017 net profit to decrease by about 38.02 percent, or to be about 110 million yuan
* Says FY 2016 net profit was 177.5 million yuan
* The main reason for the forecast is investment on cinemas, entertainment marketing, Internet platforms, concerts
